Translation

[Chorus]
Is that star looking at me too?
Won’t it be looking at me?
Is that star looking at me too?
At me?
Isn’t it looking for me right now?
Or is it avoiding me?
At me?

[Verse 1]
You’re fainter today
So this night is meaningless to me
Even if the dark night passes and morning comes
Even if I can’t see you because of the clouds
Even though I know you’re still there

[Verse 2]
Every time I can’t see you
I get nervous
So I pray that the clouds will be rain
And fall down

[Chorus]
Is that star looking at me too?
Won’t it be looking at me?
Is that star looking at me too?
At me?
Isn’t it looking for me right now?
Or is it avoiding me?
At me?

[Verse 3]
Is there anything that shines as much as you?
What if you can’t hear my song
Because you’re too far away?
What I’m looking at
Is that you?
Every night, I look at you

[Verse 4[
Did you see me with my hands gathered?
Did you see me too?
Or did you avoid me?
I pray that you’ll fall into my arms
My shooting star
I won’t ever let you go
My shining star
This is just part of the journey

[Chorus]
Is that star looking at me too?
Won’t it be looking at me?
Is that star looking at me too?
At me?
Isn’t it looking for me right now?
Or is it avoiding me?
At me?

[Bridge]
All I can do right now
Is to believe that you’re looking at me
So even after you left me
Without a single trace
But why is that I can see you
But I can’t touch you or hug you?

